                        <TABLE style="WORD-BREAK: break-all" border=0 width=650><TBODY><TR><TD><div>如图，在四棱锥P&shy;ABCD中，PD⊥平面ABCD，四边形ABCD是菱形，AC＝2，BD＝2<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140824/20140824060518439344.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" />，E是PB上任意一点．<br />(1)求证：AC⊥DE；<br />(2)已知二面角A&shy;PB&shy;D的余弦值为<img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140824/20140824060518454437.png" style="vertical-align:middle;" />，若E为PB的中点，求EC与平面PAB所成角的正弦值．<br /><img src="http://pic2.mofangge.com/upload/papers//20140824/201408240605185014053.jpg" style="vertical-align:middle;" /></div></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE>
